title: art of haven-2013-ten years in haven
description:
Art of Haven is a Hungarian melodic metal band. Ten Years in Haven is a compilation of their best instrumental songs of the past ten years.

2. the trees shall tell
3. the twilight of bygone eras
4. scenes from a life
5. through the peaks of the alps
6. a thousand years old road
7. awakening
8. reminiscence
9. forgotten
